title: VA for Instagram
job_overview:
Looking for a setter that can work specific hours (9:00 AM -5:00 PM EST, Monday-Saturday).
Must be able to speak good English, use Instagram and the DMs, follow the given framework, track leads, and KPIs.
This is a $250 PM but can make up to $1250 PM with commission and bonuses.
Looking for someone ambitious who wants to make more in commissions and bonuses than just base salary. The Potential here for you is incredible.
